  "num": 26,
  "title": "第二十六章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "重為輕根，靜為躁君。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人終日行不離輜重。"
    },
    {
      "text": "雖有榮觀，燕處超然。"
    },
    {
      "text": "奈何萬乘之主，而以身輕天下？輕則失本，躁則失君。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "凡物輕不能載重，小不能鎮大。不行者使行，不動者制動，是以重必為輕根，靜必為躁君也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以重為本，故不離。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不以經心也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "輕，不鎮重也，失本，為喪身也，失君，為失君位也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
